    \begin{equation}
        H_q = -\frac{\hbar^2}{2m_e}\nabla^2 + V_{qu}(\mathbf{r})
    \end{equation}

    \item \textbf{Interaction Potential ($V$):} Describes the coupling between the quantum state and the neural firing threshold.
